- [ ] Dynamic `src` / network ⇒ placeholder/loader lifecycle until settle.
- [ ] Carousel transitions always show discernible loaders + cohesive `aria-busy`.
- [ ] User-visible strings ⇒ dictionaries (**`09`**).
- [ ] Colors rely on semantic tokens (**`01`**).

